Part 2: User & Permission Management
Very important for Admin role 🔐
Copy code

useradd rohit
passwd rohit
usermod -aG sudo rohit
userdel rohit

groupadd devops
groupdel devops

chmod 755 file.sh
chmod +x script.sh
chown user:group file.txt
id username
who
whoami
👉 Important Concept:
777 = Full permission
755 = Owner full, others read+execute
644 = File default permission
